{"tid":1366681,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗消遣好去處-My Cinema Yoho Mall","createTime":"2019-07-26T04:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T06:16:31.000Z","uid":284429,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ca1a02b4421452e2c1b397216fc500a0b684d428","tid":1366681,"uid":284429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fTufDoS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfTufDoS.png&h=5ea592ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周未嚟元朗除左可以行街食野捉精靈之外，睇返場戲都唔錯丫。<br />\n<br />\n戲院喺正元朗西鐵站隔離個Yoho Mall入面，方便就腳又有冷氣嘆，最啱行完街身水身汗入去抖一抖啦。<br />\n<br />\n唔知睇咩好嘅推介大家睇《獅子王》啦，真實呈現經典動畫，香港有好多叔叔親自化身撕紙王落力宣傳添，真係唔睇唔得啦！"},{"pid":"8d0ec70c14bb066f78e65ffb7c1df68ae86930e6","tid":1366681,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:36:11.000Z","msg":"(喺街俾撕紙狗逗)<br />\n🐶：黎元朗做咩呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：睇撕紙王囉<br />\n🐶：咩話? (<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：獅子王呀(Show戲飛)"},{"pid":"4c3ea684400539977cddd9c6c870a8aeababf0f1","tid":1366681,"uid":27432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:37:59.000Z","msg":"OK WO, <br />\n一百幾十買張飛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a35cf945499e00e84c00626376d6b6a61cd0f0","tid":1366681,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c3ea684400539977cddd9c6c870a8aeababf0f1","tid":1366681,"uid":27432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:37:59.000Z","msg":"OK WO, <br />\n一百幾十買張飛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7ebeca6cd9f5354483649f104eef87227e39d4","tid":1366681,"uid":284429,"lik